<subSubSection id="C37642ECFFF2FFC6FA0C5BEA5C7EFBEF" pageId="31" pageNumber="583" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BD31167FFF2FFC6FA0C5BEA5C7EFBEF" blockId="31.[1454,2659,720,1226]" pageId="31" pageNumber="583">
<emphasis id="B918CD75FFF2FFC6FA0C5BEA5D6FFB90" bold="true" box="[1456,1806,995,1028]" pageId="31" pageNumber="583">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Plain Brush-tailed Rat occurs in some protected areas. Additional studies on distribution, habitat, abundance, ecology, and conservation threats to Plain Brush-tailed Rat are needed.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
